# Convivium expenses management

This is a simple piece of software realized for the management of expenses in
a small-medium group of people. 

Allow to create users assign roles and create expense groups, it include also
some reporting about expenses based on categories and credit and debit
history.

# Practical info

admin username and password:

>  user : admin
>
>  password : admin

the user is automatically created during the migration.

Moreover the application is fully compatible with [Heroku](http://www.heroku.com/).